section.works
  .container.works__container
    .works__content
      h2.title Мои работы
      .slider
        .slider__display
          .slider__display-pic
            +image('content/site-phone.jpg', ".slider__display-pic-icon")
          .slider__display-thumbs
            ul.slider-thumbs
              li.slider-thumbs__link
                a.slider-thumbs__link
                  .slider-thumbs__pic
                    +image('content/thumb_one.png', "slider-thumbs__pic-icon")
              li.slider-thumbs__link
                a.slider-thumbs__link
                  .slider-thumbs__pic
                    +image('content/thumb_two.png', "slider-thumbs__pic-icon")
              li.slider-thumbs__link
                a.slider-thumbs__link
                  .slider-thumbs__pic
                    +image('content/thumb_three.png', "slider-thumbs__pic-icon")
              li.slider-thumbs__link
                a.slider-thumbs__link
                  .slider-thumbs__pic
                    +image('content/thumb_four.png', "slider-thumbs__pic-icon")
          .slider__buttons
            a.direction-btns
              +icon('arrow-down', 'direction-btns-icon direction-btns-icon_up')
            a.direction-btns
              +icon('arrow-down', 'direction-btns-icon direction-btns-icon_down')
        .slider__info
          .slider__tags
            ul.tags
              li.tags__item Html
              li.tags__item css
              li.tags__item javascript
          .slider__info-text
            h3.slider__info-title
              |Сайт школы 
              |образования
            .slider__info-desc
              |Этот парень проходил обучение 
              br
              |веб-разработке не где-то, а в LoftSchool! 
              br
              |2 месяца только самых тяжелых 
              br
              |испытаний и бессонных ночей!
          .slider__info-btns
            +icon('link', 'slider__info-link')
            a.iconend-link Посмотреть сайт
  .triangles.triangles_budda
    svg.triangle__item(viewBox="0 0 1000 100" preserveAspectRatio="none")
      polygon(points="0,0 1000,0 1000,100")
    svg.triangle__item(viewBox="0 0 1000 100" preserveAspectRatio="none")
      polygon(points="0,0 0,100 1000,0")